text.tspan: Road incident death rate by age, World, 1990 to 2019
Death rates from road incidents by age, measured as the number of deaths per 100,000 individuals. Road
incidents include deaths from motor vehicles, motorcyclists, cyclists and pedestrians.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
